        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>+1 striking disrupting spiked chain</em> comes in a rich, green color with rose petals painted on the handle in varying shades of red and pink. The chain seems to banish nearby shadows.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You hold the chain out before you, and the weapon glows as bright as a torch. You can suppress this light by Activating the weapon again.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You critically succeed at a Strike against a fiend or undead</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The weapon unleashes its light in an attempt to destroy the target. The <em>vine of roses</em> casts a 3rd-rank @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Holy Light] spell with the triggering creature as the target. In place of a spell attack roll, make a weapon attack roll with the <em>vine of roses</em> using the same multiple attack penalty as the triggering Strike.</p>"
